{"tid":358168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭紹傑被拯溺員工會永久刪除會員資格","createTime":"2017-08-13T14:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T10:55:20.000Z","uid":33028,"like":68,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29d8384c7a83531ed8f469ea1fdb3df5b3b5c5df","tid":358168,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"曾在佔中期間在金鐘佔領區出任糾察的郭紹傑，被港九拯溺員工會永久刪除會員資格，即日生效。工會指其在病假下高調參與社會運動，違反公務員政治中立原則，又指他過去曾在未經授權下以工會代表發言。<br />\n<br />\n港九拯溺員工會在facebook發表聲明，指郭紹傑在任工會理事期間，在領取工傷病假下，高調參與社會運動，違反公務員必須保持政治中立原則及誠信，引起大部份會員不滿，及至影響救生員行業聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n同時，工會又指郭紹傑未經理事會批準，經勸喻後，仍多次聲稱代表工會接受傳媒訪問，違反工會內部指引，嚴重影響本會之誠信及公信力。<br />\n<br />\n因此，工會經內部會議後，將永久删除郭紹傑在工會內會員資格，即日生效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lifeguardsunion.org/posts/1539005436122930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flifeguardsunion.org%2Fposts%2F1539005436122930&d=t46%2FtfowoK8Q2COlZByiL1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=97dde3f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lifeguardsunion.org/posts/1539005436122930</a>"},{"pid":"32d4e1f2482b64f96687d4ae108e32ca02fbbb43","tid":358168,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb29d4aa2b313a22466eb3882a3d0037c741085","tid":358168,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:03:46.000Z","msg":"條友工傷呃咗幾多人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5aa51bf5bb70fec42ea25d8e19ee51421550926","tid":358168,"uid":81052,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"公務員政治中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a7b2d1ab68a1725d58510728ee068504d975db","tid":358168,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":